title: The Millionaire Fastlane: Crack the Code to Wealth and Live Rich
description:
Format: ePub

DRM stripped in Calibre.

Have you prostituted your Monday through Friday for the paycheck of a weekend? Hope aboard the expressway to extraordinary wealth and make everyday your weekend.
There's a Fastlane to millions, a short-cut paved by entrepreneurial mathematics where you can LIVE RICH NOW versus DYING RICH LATER. 
Instead, you've been brainwashed by an army of financial "experts" who pitch a dream-killing dogma known as "get rich slow". 
Their lifelong, suffocating plan of mediocrity promises elderly riches by recklessly gambling your financial future on the stock market, the housing market, and the job market. Reject hope-and-pray as a financial plan; switch lanes, and discover how Fastlane Entrepreneurship can squash mediocrity and resurrect your dreams to reality.
